⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Triforce
node ZEL · ZEL · ⟦The Triforce:ZEL:000dde⟧

WHO   — The Triforce — the divine relic
WHAT  — The sacred golden relic of the Goddesses — three triangles of Power, Wisdom, and Courage — that grants the wish of whoever touches it, and splits to seek out chosen bearers when the heart is unbalanced.
WHERE — ZEL · The Legend of Zelda  Framework inputs: The Legend of Zelda (the saga entire)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the Goddesses left their power behind when they departed the world; because such power answers any wish, for light or for shadow; because when no single heart holds all three in balance, the relic divides itself and chooses its bearers across the ages.
HOW   — By the gift of the three who made the world — Din's power, Nayru's wisdom, Farore's courage — left as one golden mark in the Sacred Realm; by granting the wish of the hand that claims it; by splitting into its three when the claimant's heart is unbalanced, marking the chosen until the pieces are gathered again.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the wish the world was left to hold — three triangles, one light, granted to the hand that proves worthy and splitting where the heart is not.

spoken token : vaeth-rand-xom   ·   hex : 000dde
